Terrorsaur:





Terrorsaur turned his head to KitKat. "We go around," he said to her. "From 
my scanners he may be a few sections away. Two up, then right. I think." He 
turned to Drillbit. "That's where you come in." He pressed his hands against 
the wall of the cave. "I want you to lead the way. Here. And make sure you 
don't break into the water."
